title: Petition/Application Was Rejected For Insufficient Funds
body: On April 5, 2021, we rejected your Form I-824, Application for Action on an Approved Application or Petition, Receipt Number YSC2190118711 because your filing fee was returned by your financial institution for insufficient funds. Any previously assigned priority or processing date is no longer applicable. If you wish to still pursue the benefit, you must file a new application or petition and submit a new fee filing fee. If you need assistance, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you change your mailing address, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
